.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fBDoppel\fR recursively copies files from a given directory and compiles all templates in the directory copy\.
.
.SH "OPTIONS"
.
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Prints the current \fBdoppel\fR version\.
